{"type":"answer","id":99834,"parentType":"question","parentId":12887,"uid":9922,"contents":"<b>举世皆浊我独清，众人皆醉我独醒。</b><br>\n<br>\n<blockquote>1936年6月13日，海军训练船霍斯特·威塞尔号启航，福斯船厂的一名工人拒绝行纳粹礼，他的举动被人拍了下来，因而使他闻名于世。</blockquote><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/A38UzgG.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A38UzgG.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/A38UzgG.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-09","agreeCount":35,"discussionCount":0}